hint.googleSheet.requirements.alert:
To import data successfully, your Google Sheet must meet the following requirements:
- the sheet is publicly accessible (Anyone with the link — Viewer);
- the "First Name" column is present;
- the "Last Name" column is present;
- the "Weight" column is present (numeric value);
- the "Tournament Categories" column is present;
- the "Tournament Categories" field lists category names separated by commas;
- each tournament category name contains a unique category identifier;
